entities.createSql: CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `${TABLE_NAME}` (`rowid` INTEGER PRIMARY KEY AUTOINCREMENT NOT NULL, `ssid` TEXT NOT NULL, `networkId` INTEGER NOT NULL, `securityTypes` TEXT NOT NULL, `password` TEXT NOT NULL, `hidden` INTEGER NOT NULL, `autojoin` INTEGER NOT NULL, `private` INTEGER NOT NULL, `note` TEXT)
CREATE VIRTUAL TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `${TABLE_NAME}` USING FTS4(`ssid` TEXT NOT NULL, `note` TEXT NOT NULL, content=`wifi_networks`)
contentSyncTriggers: CREATE TRIGGER IF NOT EXISTS room_fts_content_sync_wifi_networks_fts_BEFORE_UPDATE BEFORE UPDATE ON `wifi_networks` BEGIN DELETE FROM `wifi_networks_fts` WHERE `docid`=OLD.`rowid`; END
CREATE TRIGGER IF NOT EXISTS room_fts_content_sync_wifi_networks_fts_BEFORE_DELETE BEFORE DELETE ON `wifi_networks` BEGIN DELETE FROM `wifi_networks_fts` WHERE `docid`=OLD.`rowid`; END

CREATE TRIGGER IF NOT EXISTS room_fts_content_sync_wifi_networks_fts_AFTER_UPDATE AFTER UPDATE ON `wifi_networks` BEGIN INSERT INTO `wifi_networks_fts`(`docid`, `ssid`, `note`) VALUES (NEW.`rowid`, NEW.`ssid`, NEW.`note`); END

CREATE TRIGGER IF NOT EXISTS room_fts_content_sync_wifi_networks_fts_AFTER_INSERT AFTER INSERT ON `wifi_networks` BEGIN INSERT INTO `wifi_networks_fts`(`docid`, `ssid`, `note`) VALUES (NEW.`rowid`, NEW.`ssid`, NEW.`note`); END
